entries.femaleVariant: So Rogue knew all about Alt. But Alt...?
You guessed Rogue worked for the corps – how'd you do it?
[pl_pl]Nie przeszkadza ci, że sypiam z Kerrym?
entries.maleVariant: Me sleeping with Kerry – you cool with that?

entries.femaleVariant: So, Rogue knew about Alt. What about Alt...?
You knew Rogue was running for the corps – but how?

entries.maleVariant: Hey, um, you cool with me sleeping with Kerry?

entries.femaleVariant: D'she know about Rogue?

entries.maleVariant: Wanna talk about that, you gotta start thinkin' larger scale – much larger. Alt and Rogue – tip of the assberg.

entries.femaleVariant: And what about his old flame Anna Maria, her fire smothered as she languored helplessly in virtuspace?
Antonio, fifty years in a coma, wakes up to find he's a woman! Can he forgive Manuela her infidelity?
Yeah. That's what I wanna know.
Fuck me, V. So do I.

entries.maleVariant: Oh, come on – "sleeping with him?" He fucked you once, end of story.
Wouldn't get used to it if I were you.
Kerry used to spend all kinds of time and energy tryin' to get me into bed with him.
A little ironic, actually, that he finally got what he wanted thanks to you.
Wow, you do know it's not always about you? That thought ever enter your mind?
Hm. Nope, that's a new one.

entries.femaleVariant: Corps practically wiped the Afterlife off this city's face. Rogue was the last denizen standing. Who kept her afloat?
Just that?
That and the Smasher thing. Rogue said it herself – prick was just the tip of the iceberg.
Grayson knew her, knew she'd worked for Smasher.
And if she worked for Smasher, she was open to working for anybody.
Imagined your reunion with Alt differently, I bet.
Prolly not how you pictured your grand reunion with Alt.
I knew she'd change, transform... All started when she went silicon, hit the net.
You've changed too.
Wanted to talk about something else.
You've changed too, you're someone else.
Wanted to broach another topic.
I've had fuck all to do with it. Alt's out there fractaling, globulating, becoming a bigger and better AI.
And I'm here shriveling, spendin' time with you.
Thought she might still throw her arms around you?
Did ya think she'd throw her arms around your neck?
Thought we'd talk… truly, madly, deeply – like we used to way back when.
Ah, you're bitter.
And fix what you fucked up? Or prove something to her?
As in make a scene and manipulate her?
Got her on board, that's all that matters.
Wanted to talk about something else.
To fix what you busted? Or to prove somethin' to 'er?
Mean, like, making a scene, manipulating 'er?
Guess I just never thought she'd stop giving a fuck about me so completely.
You got her on board – that's what matters.
Got her to help us, you did – only thing that matters.
Doesn't give a lick about helping me. Wants to wipe Mikoshi.
No, she feels accountable for how Arasaka used Soulkiller. That's why she's coming.
And it took you to remind her of that, only you.
Hm. Could be.
Say what you want, that was real. Human.
More like, prove myself wrong. Dead wrong when I told her we had nothing, were nothing and shared nothing but sex.
That was long ago, talkin' decades.
Not to me. Don't forget, I've spent the last fifty years stuck in my head.
Doesn't matter. Seems I'm about fifty years late in gettin' to it.
